<h1>About {{ site.title }}</h1>
<p>Juniper & Tonic cuts through the marketing hype to deliver thoughtful, independent reviews of craft and classic gins from around the world. We evaluate each spirit on its botanical balance, distillation quality, and versatility in cocktails and neat sipping. Our tastings are conducted blind whenever possible, ensuring unbiased assessments that help you discover gins worth adding to your home bar. Whether you're a seasoned gin enthusiast or just beginning to explore beyond the mainstream, we're here to guide your botanical journey.</p>
<p style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px;">
Reviews on this site synthesize publicly available research and reflect one perspective on each product.
Scoring categories and weights are chosen per product to fit what matters for that item.
</p>
